data.text: Aspiration is the #keyword of CEAir in #2021. Looking back at 2021, #CEAir has left many wonderful, touching and inspiring moments. Looking forward to #2022, we will strive for the best in our positions to write a more extraordinary chapter! #MUStory https://t.co/H5haZWLUIx

data.text: ❄️Today is one of the #24solarterms, Major Snow (Daxue). During Major Snow, the snow becomes heavy and begins to accumulate on the ground. Everything becomes covered in snow, and a winter wonderland of snowflakes comes. Do you want to have a romantic date with #CEAir? https://t.co/oT4ao5wB4u

✈️To all civil aviation workers, happy #InternationalCivilAviationDay from #CEAir! In the future, let's continue to work hard to guard our aviation dreams. Looking forward to a better future for our industry! @icao https://t.co/mHPxTgemsO
✈️Flying through the blue sky and white clouds, greet the bright #morning light with #CEAir. Today is another day full of hope! https://t.co/iSsnFEx6C1

#Nanjing, a city full of stories. Beautiful natural landscape, cultural attractions and historic sites and the booming modern civilization... Click on the video below, and experience the fascinating blend of the old and the new of this city! #TravelwithCEAir @DiscoverNanjing https://t.co/nvk6QhKDeb

⛩️The Confucius Temple was the first higher educational institution in China and was built to commemorate Confucius. Just a short step away from the temple is the Qinhuai River, from where romantic stories always reach your ears.
#TravelwithCEAir @DiscoverNanjing https://t.co/5Wx2SvovvA

WOW! Today is #20211202. What a symmetric day! 
Reply with a palindrome in the comments! https://t.co/AApTApNDVL

The Monkey King is coming! The Huaguo Mountain themed aircraft is my reincarnation! Today is my first flight from #Lianyungang #Huaguoshan Airport to #Beijing #Daxing Airport. Let's see how I fly through the clouds and realize my flying dream! https://t.co/S0vT0c4hUk

✈️#CEAir’s intl "passenger-to-cargo" charter flight took off from #Wenzhou, #China and flew to #Milan, #Italy on Nov. 29.  In addition to flying to Milan on Mondays and Wednesdays, this airplane will also fly from Wenzhou to #LosAngeles on Fridays and Saturdays. https://t.co/Y43EFRTGcw
